      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Beastly Chaos",
        "Client": "Distressed Felyne",
        "Description": "Oh meow! A Tigrex and a Goss\r\nHarag are going berserk out in\r\nthe Frost Islands! If someone\r\ndoesn\u0027t stop \u0027em, the island\u0027s\r\ngonna get carved up like a\r\nscratching post! Help!",
